HEADWORD: New-year
<hw>New"-year`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to, or suitable for, the commencement of the year; <as>as,
<ex>New-year</ex> gifts or odes</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>New Year's Day</ent>⟦br⟧
